	                                                TextureCoordinates="0.6667,0 0.6667,1 0.8333,0 0.8333,0 0.6667,1 0.8333,1 0.8333,0 0.8333,1 1,0 1,0 0.8333,1 1,1 0.3333,0 0.3333,1 0.5,0 0.5,0 0.3333,1 0.5,1 0.5,0 0.5,1 0.6667,0 0.6667,0 0.5,1
